{
  "texts": [
    "In order to illustrate some of these tools on a real dataset, we will present results on a benchmark dataset for Human Papilloma Virus (HPV) status prediction in head and neck squamous cell carcinoma.",
    "The training/validation dataset is comprised of 262 patients (151 HPVnegative, 111 HPV-positive) from the University of Chicago, and the held-out external dataset is comprised of 459 patients (407 HPV-negative, 52 HPV-positive) across 26 sites from The Cancer Genome Atlas (TCGA).",
    "All patients had one associated WSI.",
    "Slide processingPathologists annotated ROIs encircling areas of tumor for all slides, except in cases where the entire sample was determined to be tumor.",
    "Otsu and Gaussian blur filtering were explored for this dataset."
  ]
}